      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用毫秒级，从T0开始。安全模块要标注在括号里，紧跟在对应步骤后面。比如JWT验证那一步，要注明Security_IntrusionDetection。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T0ms",
